{"tid":365053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"做唔一定成功﹐但乜都唔做就一定唔會成功","createTime":"2017-08-19T02:40:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T03:54:38.000Z","uid":37656,"like":29,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"db11a5ed586191f7382fab0b83c6c510376d9576","tid":365053,"uid":37656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T02:40:26.000Z","msg":"自己覺得點做先有用就點做<br />\n乜都唔做﹐呢個世界係唔會改變"},{"pid":"e7e978bf9ad105ee1ddff1dd31ebe1d3051c3d27","tid":365053,"uid":23170,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T02:41:29.000Z","msg":"好啱，道理雖淺但係唔係個個都明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61ae30e331c91bc1161c26f381c3bb54741d1062","tid":365053,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T02:49:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5524c95278a0338b1d8a704adec9927abe14c314","tid":365053,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T02:49:49.000Z","msg":"就係唔知點做有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f83398cde694de258c04cbe3716bb3dd10839a14","tid":365053,"uid":65128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T02:52:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0bf3cf418b2c898fe2632a144277c8be71ff962e","tid":365053,"uid":37656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T03:03:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就係唔知點做有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你啱呀﹐我都唔知點做先有用﹐知就做左啦﹐係咪？<br />\n自己諗唔到﹐咪揀d 人地諗到而你又唔反對既野去做囉﹐跟自己理念去決定<br />\n<br />\n要成功就靠機會﹐但機會係要靠自己去尋找<br />\n<br />\n唔好講政治﹐溝女﹑讀書﹑工作咪又係一樣<br />\n有人個樣咁柒都溝到女<br />\n有人温左兩頁書考試就合格<br />\n有人做唔到野但又上左位<br />\n呢d 人既成功之前﹐你估佢地知唔知自己一定掂？"},{"pid":"5b05a62ebc8f49c763750216332a826036756718","tid":365053,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T03:23:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>就係唔知點做有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你啱呀﹐我都唔知點做先有用﹐知就做左啦﹐係咪？<br />\n自己諗唔到﹐咪揀d 人地諗到而你又唔反對既野去做囉﹐跟自己理念去決定<br />\n<br />\n要成功就靠機會﹐但機會係要靠自己去尋找<br />\n<br />\n唔好講政治﹐溝女﹑讀書﹑工作咪又係一樣<br />\n有人個樣咁柒都溝到女<br />\n有人温左兩頁書考試就合格<br />\n有人做唔到野但又上左位<br />\n呢d 人既成功之前﹐你估佢地知唔知自己一定掂？</blockquote><br />\n好多人溝唔到女比人笑一世, <br />\n好多人溫成年書都唔合格<br />\n好多人做一世都上唔到位<br />\n唔可以只睇人地成功有收獲, 都要睇失敗既後果<br />\n<br />\n這些機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBTW, 巴打有人生拼勁好欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2bbb46c9cf4b420b6f144b08d54676bd7a6deb3","tid":365053,"uid":17531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T03:34:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9d9d68ef8ffb9e357cb833674095e69fceecf68","tid":365053,"uid":37656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T03:37:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同我堅持買六合彩嘅諗法一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買六合彩係唔需要努力﹐你唔好混為一談"},{"pid":"59bfb2b176136651cc1ef46475a2352baeafba54","tid":365053,"uid":37656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T03:42:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>就係唔知點做有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你啱呀﹐我都唔知點做先有用﹐知就做左啦﹐係咪？<br />\n自己諗唔到﹐咪揀d 人地諗到而你又唔反對既野去做囉﹐跟自己理念去決定<br />\n<br />\n要成功就靠機會﹐但機會係要靠自己去尋找<br />\n<br />\n唔好講政治﹐溝女﹑讀書﹑工作咪又係一樣<br />\n有人個樣咁柒都溝到女<br />\n有人温左兩頁書考試就合格<br />\n有人做唔到野但又上左位<br />\n呢d 人既成功之前﹐你估佢地知唔知自己一定掂？</blockquote><br />\n好多人溝唔到女比人笑一世, <br />\n好多人溫成年書都唔合格<br />\n好多人做一世都上唔到位<br />\n唔可以只睇人地成功有收獲, 都要睇失敗既後果<br />\n<br />\n這些機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBTW, 巴打有人生拼勁好欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有失敗好正常﹐唔失敗點顯得成功既珍貴﹐咁容易成功就唔需要你去努力啦<br />\n<br />\n你可以選擇渾渾噩噩﹑庸庸碌碌過一生﹐無人會怪責你"},{"pid":"f8b6af6cc6298bfee15c2f9fe90bf1445f6b51be","tid":365053,"uid":37656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T03:42:58.000Z","msg":"最緊要過到自己嗰關﹐唔會後悔你而家做緊既事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da23ae87fd913c11e5a7e38effebfd1dca1d276d","tid":365053,"uid":3713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T03:51:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同我堅持買六合彩嘅諗法一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買六合彩係唔需要努力﹐你唔好混為一談</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解買六合彩唔要努力，你要中要有恒心去買去對號碼，樣樣都係要做先成功！<br />\n唔好因為有賭博成份就沒殺買六合彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9777641617a79d2f6fce0ad626265acb0110926","tid":365053,"uid":27728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T05:27:23.000Z","msg":"呢句野害死幾多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eeceb2baf517f53713ed45ed2204d6bb69cfda6","tid":365053,"uid":37656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T05:35:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢句野害死幾多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱<br />\n<br />\n書唔好讀 女唔好溝 野唔好食 工唔好做<br />\n喺屋企等死就可以了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3476d89ce1ce984748772fcea886fe59a5dda143","tid":365053,"uid":27049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T05:37:02.000Z","msg":"努力不一定成功 但不努力會很輕鬆"},{"pid":"9f0cf65829b238dbb227e6525a81647074a3de3a","tid":365053,"uid":37656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T05:43:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>努力不一定成功 但不努力會很輕鬆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\